## Flow Captured in Video

1. **Homepage Load** (0-3s) — Video background hero section loads, navigation visible
2. **Services Navigation** (3-8s) — Click to Services page, scroll through pricing tiers
3. **Projects Gallery** (8-15s) — Projects page loads, filter buttons visible, click residential filter
4. **Contact Page** (15-20s) — Navigate to contact form, show form fields
5. **Navigation Test** (20-30s) — Return to homepage, test navigation back to services via link

